  "description": "<i>Saber Marionette J: Battle Sabers</i> is a one-on-one fighting game featuring the android characters from the anime with the same name. You get to pick from any of the 7 characters available to duke it out with your opponent in either CPU mode (1 player) or VS mode (2 players).<br><br>Before each battle you get to pick two special abilities, which all do different things. These are: Spark Punches, Fire Punches, Big hands, High Jump, Float, Big feet, Spark Kicks, Fire Kicks and they all make your character look different and they affect the way you fight in the game.",
